\\left(a^{2} x^{4}+2 a b x^{2}+b^{2}\\right)+\\left(a^{2} x^{2}-2 a c x+c^{2}\\right)+1=0 \\\\
\\left(a x^{2}+b\\right)^{2}+(a x-c)^{2}+1=0
