$$x_{1}^{3}+x_{2}^{3} = \\left(x_{1}+x_{2}\\right)\\left( x_{1}^{2}-x_{1} x_{2}+x_{2}^{2} \\right )= -1(1-2p-p) = 3p-1 = -16.$$ 

